#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:1
msgid "E4200"
msgstr "E4200"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `struct_constr_incorrect_return_type`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`struct_constr_incorrect_return_type`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:5
msgid ""
"A struct constructor must return the struct type itself. If the "
"constructor signature returns another type, the declaration cannot be "
"used as that struct's constructor."
msgstr "结构体构造器必须返回结构体自身的类型。如果构造器签名返回其他类型，这个声明就不能作为该结构体的构造器使用。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:9
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:11
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct Point {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn Point::Point(_: Int) -> String {\n"
"  \"\"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:15
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:17
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Make the constructor return the struct type and implement the matching "
"`Type::Type` function."
msgstr "让构造器返回结构体类型，并实现匹配的 `Type::new` 方法。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4200.md:20
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv struct Point {\n"
"  x : Int\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn Point::Point(x : Int) -> Point {\n"
"  { x, }\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let point = Point(1)\n"
"  inspect(point.x, content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
